1
00:00:20,570 --> 00:00:23,104
Let me go! I’m not going. Let go!

2
00:00:23,136 --> 00:00:24,864
Let me go right now! I didn't do it.

3
00:00:24,904 --> 00:00:26,656
I told you, I didn't do it!

4
00:00:27,130 --> 00:00:27,784
Let go!

5
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:30,048
Let me go!

6
00:00:30,080 --> 00:00:31,216
Hold on.

7
00:00:33,940 --> 00:00:34,968
Let go of me this instant!

8
00:00:36,320 --> 00:00:37,672
I didn't do it, everyone!

9
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:42,816
It was Ranya. Ranya did it all by herself!

10
00:00:42,848 --> 00:00:45,088
She already confessed that she did it alone!

11
00:00:45,128 --> 00:00:46,656
I didn't do anything at all, I swear!

12
00:00:47,060 --> 00:00:49,440
Everyone, I am so truly sorry.

13
00:00:49,472 --> 00:00:50,848
I know what happened was wrong.

14
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,920
I apologize.

15
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:54,600
I made a mistake, can you all please forgive me?

16
00:00:54,648 --> 00:00:56,016
I am so, so sorry!

17
00:00:56,048 --> 00:00:58,020
It was Ranya... Ranya did it all on her own!

18
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,280
I didn't do a thing.

19
00:00:59,320 --> 00:01:00,632
I am truly sorry to everyone.

20
00:01:00,672 --> 00:01:02,808
I’m sorry... I’m so sorry.

21
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:06,016
I didn't do it. I didn't do it!

22
00:01:06,910 --> 00:01:08,792
Mom... did you never even love me?

23
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:13,960
You’re just stupid!

24
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:16,256
You’ve ruined everything.

25
00:01:16,550 --> 00:01:18,248
Why should I even bother being nice to you, huh?

26
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:23,400
The only reason I ever raised you was for this company!

27
00:01:24,650 --> 00:01:27,904
I have evidence that Ranya had nothing to do with this.

28
00:01:29,608 --> 00:01:31,610
I’d like to speak with Ranya for a moment, please.

29
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:37,400
But Pimchat... I didn’t do it!

30
00:01:38,110 --> 00:01:39,632
I loved Khun Wichai so much,

31
00:01:39,656 --> 00:01:41,904
how could I ever do something like that?

32
00:01:41,928 --> 00:01:43,448
Don't you remember the funeral?

33
00:01:43,488 --> 00:01:45,320
I was devastated.

34
00:01:45,360 --> 00:01:46,624
I didn't do it!

35
00:02:21,090 --> 00:02:22,576
Ran, why are you taking the fall for her?

36
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:24,808
Don't you see?

37
00:02:26,810 --> 00:02:29,008
She doesn’t love you the way you love her.

38
00:02:31,690 --> 00:02:32,984
I’m sorry...

39
00:02:33,970 --> 00:02:35,136
It’s all my fault.

40
00:02:51,632 --> 00:02:52,576
It’s okay.

41
00:02:55,090 --> 00:02:56,504
You can let her go now, Ran.

42
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,080
It’s my fault.

43
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,712
I was so stupid.

44
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:09,416
Stop blaming yourself.

45
00:03:17,216 --> 00:03:18,544
You're my brave girl.

46
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:27,320
From now on, no matter what happens,

47
00:03:30,010 --> 00:03:31,736
don’t run away again, okay?

48
00:03:34,968 --> 00:03:37,424
We’re going to fight this together.

49
00:03:42,170 --> 00:03:43,840
Can you promise me that?

50
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:23,752
K’Wichai’s death wasn't an accident after all.

51
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:26,280
The medicine was swapped by K’Jintana.

52
00:04:26,710 --> 00:04:28,072
This was a murder.

53
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:39,176
If it's about the work plan, I’m not mad at you at all.

54
00:04:41,910 --> 00:04:43,560
In fact, I’m the one who should apologize.

55
00:04:45,620 --> 00:04:47,712
You’ve done so much for me,

56
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:51,232
yet I still failed to trust you.

57
00:04:53,810 --> 00:04:55,288
I understand.

58
00:04:57,980 --> 00:05:02,896
Honestly, I was just more afraid that you’d be mad.

59
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:12,472
Is something wrong?

60
00:05:16,192 --> 00:05:16,888
Nothing,

61
00:05:18,670 --> 00:05:19,864
Eat up.

62
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:34,696
The cause of K’Wichai’s death wasn't an accident.

63
00:05:37,230 --> 00:05:41,400
My mother was the one who planned the whole thing.

64
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:09,056
Why did Jintana have to kill you?

65
00:06:16,100 --> 00:06:18,944
Dad, I can’t even look at Ranya’s face anymore.

66
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:31,536
P'Chat,

67
00:06:35,264 --> 00:06:37,260
may I come in?

68
00:07:00,260 --> 00:07:01,568
...Fine, that’s okay.

69
00:07:04,552 --> 00:07:06,296
I’ll wait for you right here.

70
00:07:08,912 --> 00:07:10,910
I'll wait until you’re ready to talk to me.

71
00:07:50,260 --> 00:07:51,640
I understand...

72
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:55,896
Everyone loves their own father.

73
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:00,120
I have no excuses at all.

74
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,928
I am truly sorry.

75
00:08:05,056 --> 00:08:07,060
I’m so sorry for what my mother did.

76
00:08:19,580 --> 00:08:21,200
Chat loves Dad very much...

77
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:25,440
but I love you very much too, Ranya.

78
00:08:29,900 --> 00:08:31,680
Dad isn't upset with me, is he?

79
00:08:40,136 --> 00:08:42,140
I know you didn't do anything wrong.

80
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,688
But I still just can't bring myself to fully trust you yet.

81
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,304
It’s okay.

82
00:09:04,210 --> 00:09:05,576
I understand.

83
00:09:08,380 --> 00:09:10,544
Even though you helped me with everything,

84
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,040
I still...

85
00:09:13,064 --> 00:09:14,256
If it were me,

86
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,160
I probably would have lost it way more than you did.

87
00:09:24,980 --> 00:09:26,728
You’ve been so strong.

88
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,224
From now on,

89
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:45,080
let’s do it together to make things right.

90
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:49,400
We’ll get through this together, okay?

91
00:09:51,810 --> 00:09:55,496
Thank you for giving me a chance.

92
00:09:57,860 --> 00:09:59,376
It's a chance for both of us.

93
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:09,936
K’Pimprapha, K’Wichai...

94
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,336
After this,

95
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:25,536
I will take care of P'Chat as best as I possibly can.

96
00:10:37,260 --> 00:10:39,184
And I’ll take care of her, too.

97
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:45,584
As long as I has her here in the company, I’m not afraid of anything anymore.

98
00:10:53,864 --> 00:10:55,056
Thank you.

99
00:10:57,430 --> 00:10:59,224
I love you the most.

100
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:03,888
I love you too, Ranya.
